name: Alpha SEO Consultancy
overview:
As a small London based SEO Consultancy firm, we are primarily focused on helping local businesses to establish a viable online presence and to dominate their particular sector of the market. In order to achieve this, we offer a very individual seo consultancy service that analyses the specific requirements that you, the client, have and creates a bespoke package that will meet those needs and ultimately serve you best, in accordance with your budget. Alternatively, you can choose from our selection of fixed SEO Consultancy packages which have been designed to cater for both short and long-term seo campaigns or select from one of the additional services we have to offer. Specialties

Search Engine Optimisation for Local Business, Social Media Marketing for Local Business, Mobile Ready Sites, Small Business SEO, LinkedIn Optimisation, Local SEO, Build a facebook fanpage, On-page SEO, Off-page SEO
